\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li77\ri48\sb293\sl-298\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw-5\f1\fs24 Bu eser, enerjiyi ve onun ya\'fe\lang1031\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 za katt\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  iyi y\f1\'f6\f0 nleri a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 klamak amac\f1\'fd\f0 ndad\f1\'fd\f0 r. Ki\f1\'fe\f0 inin ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0 na y\f1\'f6\f0 n vermesi i\f1\'e7\f0 in tarafs\f1\'fd\f0 z, enerjiyle \f1\'e7\f0 al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 may\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 renip ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'fc\f0 zerinde s\f1\'f6\f0 z sa\-\expndtw-4 hibi olabilmesi i\f1\'e7\f0 in de g\f1\'fc\f0 nl\f1\'fc\f0 k ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 za uygulamas\f1\'fd\f0  kolay \expndtw-5 ve basit \f1\'f6\f0 neriler sunuyor. Asl\f1\'fd\f0 nda, enerjiyi ke\f1\'fe\f0 fetmek, ayn\f1\'fd \expndtw-4\f0 zamanda kendini tan\f1\'fd\f0 mak demektir!\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
