\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li101\ri10\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw3\fs22 Bize en yak\'fd\lang1031\f0 n olan \f1\'f6\f0 rnek, Yahudilerin Kutsal Kitap me\-\expndtw7 tinleri ve s\f1\'f6\f0 zl\f1\'fc\f0  gelenekleri \f1\'fc\f0 zerine yapt\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  gizemli yorum \expndtw2 olan Kabala, ayn\f1\'fd\f0  enerjiye "y\f1\'fd\f0 ld\f1\'fd\f0 zsal \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k" der. H\f1\'fd\f0 ristiyanl\f1\'fd\f0 kta \expndtw4 da, \f1\'e7\f0 ok say\f1\'fd\f0 daki resimde ve ikonda bulunan \f1\'dd\f0 sa ve di\f1\'f0\f0 er dini \expndtw2 ki\f1\'fe\f0 iler, bu \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 kl\f1\'fd\f0  alanla \f1\'e7\f0 evrelenmi\f1\'fe\f0  olarak g\f1\'f6\f0 sterilirler. Eski\-\expndtw4 den, k\f1\'fc\'e7\'fc\f0 k din kitaplar\f1\'fd\f0 nda, bu olay azizlerin ba\f1\'fe\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 ndaki haleler (aura) ile a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 klan\f1\'fd\f0 rd\f1\'fd\f0 . Petit Larousse' a g\f1\'f6\f0 z att\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 z\-da \f1\'fe\f0 u a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 klamayla kar\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 la\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 r\f1\'fd\f0 z: Latince aureoa'dan gelen hale \expndtw3 kelimesi, alt\f1\'fd\f0 n ta\f1\'e7\f0  (Latince \i corona) \i0 demektir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li154\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22 G\'f6\lang1031\f0 rd\f1\'fc\'f0\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0 z gibi bu enerji, \f1\'e7\f0 ok eski zamanlardan beri \expndtw2 g\f1\'f6\f0 zlenmi\f1\'fe\f0  ve de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 ik isimlerle an\f1\'fd\f0 lm\f1\'fd\'fe\f0  olsa da, anlam\f1\'fd\f0  tektir-, \expndtw4 evrensel enerji alan\f1\'fd\f0 .\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
