\pard\cbpat2\fi398\ri48\sb312\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\fs22 E\'f0\lang1031\f0 er maddeyi, yo\f1\'f0\f0 unla\f1\'fe\f0 m\f1\'fd\'fe\f0  enerji olarak tan\f1\'fd\f0 mlarsak, \expndtw4 evrensel enerji alan\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  da maddeyle enerjinin b\f1\'f6\f0 lgeleri ara\-\expndtw2 s\f1\'fd\f0 nda yer ald\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  varsayarak a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 klayabiliriz.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li5\ri34\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw2\fs22 Evrensel enerji alan\'fd\lang1031\f0 , b\f1\'fc\f0 t\f1\'fc\f0 n uzay\f1\'fd\f0 n, canl\f1\'fd\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n oldu\f1\'f0\f0 u ka\-dar cans\f1\'fd\f0 z cisimlerin de i\f1\'e7\f0 ine i\f1\'fe\f0 lemi\f1\'fe\f0  bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde ve bu cisim\-\expndtw3 lerle aram\f1\'fd\f0 zda yer al\f1\'fd\f0 r. Kaynak noktas\f1\'fd\f0 yla aras\f1\'fd\f0 ndaki uzakl\f1\'fd\-\expndtw5\'f0\f0 a g\f1\'f6\f0 re de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 en bir yo\f1\'f0\f0 unlukla, bir cisimden di\f1\'f0\f0 erine hare\-\expndtw3 ket eder. K\f1\'fc\'e7\'fc\f0 k enerji iplerini hat\f1\'fd\f0 rlad\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z m\f1\'fd\f0 ? Bu alan, d\f1\'fc\-\expndtw1\f0 zenli ind\f1\'fc\f0 kleme" ve paralel rezonans\super 12\nosupersub ' yasalar\f1\'fd\f0 na uyar, yani, \expndtw2 diyapozonu\super 131\nosupersub  t\f1\'fd\f0 nlatt\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 zda, kendisi de, ayn\f1\'fd\f0  sesi \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 kar\f1\'fd\f0 p, \expndtw3 ayn\f1\'fd\f0  frekansta t\f1\'fd\f0 nlayacakt\f1\'fd\f0 r.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li24\ri19\sb5\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\fs22 Ara\'fe\lang1031\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 rmac\f1\'fd\f0 lar evrensel enerji alan\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n, birbirinden ayr\f1\'fd \expndtw4\f0 ve farkl\f1\'fd\f0  frekansta titre\f1\'fe\f0 en \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k noktalar\f1\'fd\f0 ndan, spirallerden, \expndtw2 birbirine ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'e7\f0 izgilerden olu\f1\'fe\f0 mu\f1\'fe\f0  bir dizi \f1\'e7\f0 ok iyi d\f1\'fc\f0 zenlen\-\expndtw3 mi\f1\'fe\f0  geometrik noktadan, ayn\f1\'fd\f0  zamanda da k\f1\'fd\f0 v\f1\'fd\f0 lc\f1\'fd\f0 m ve bu\f1\'f0\f0 u\-\expndtw5 dan olu\f1\'fe\f0 tu\f1\'f0\f0 unu ileri s\f1\'fc\f0 rerler. Bu alan dokunarak, tadarak, \expndtw2 koklayarak ve i\f1\'fe\f0 iterek alg\f1\'fd\f0 lanabilen titre\f1\'fe\f0 imler yayar. Parlak\-\expndtw1 l\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 , en zay\f1\'fd\f0 f duyularla dahi fark edilebilir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
