\pard\cbpat2\fi384\li48\sl-298\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw2\fs22\'c7\lang1031\f0 imlere yatar durumdayken, bak\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  mavi g\f1\'f6\f0 ky\f1\'fc\f0 z\f1\'fc\-\expndtw3\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 n alt\f1\'fd\f0 ndaki a\f1\'f0\f0 a\f1\'e7\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n tepelerine y\f1\'f6\f0 neltin. A\f1\'f0\f0 a\f1\'e7\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n \f1\'e7\f0 evre\-sinde, ye\f1\'fe\f0 ilimsi bir bu\f1\'f0\f0 u g\f1\'f6\f0 receksiniz. E\f1\'f0\f0 er, mavi g\f1\'f6\f0 kte k\f1\'fc\-\expndtw2\'e7\'fc\f0 k enerji k\f1\'fc\f0 reciklerini g\f1\'f6\f0 rd\f1\'fc\f0 yseniz, \f1\'fe\'fc\f0 phesiz bunlar\f1\'fd\f0 n ye\f1\'fe\f0 il \expndtw6 bu\f1\'f0\f0 uda kayboldu\f1\'f0\f0 unu da fark edeceksiniz. G\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 ld\f1\'fc\'f0\'fc\f0  gibi,\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
