\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li43\ri43\sb307\sl-298\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\b\fs22 Birinci i\'fe\lang1031\f0 levi: \b0 Evrensel enerji alan\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n enerjisini y\f1\'f6\f0 n\-\expndtw1 lendirerek fiziksel v\f1\'fc\f0 cudun canland\f1\'fd\f0 r\f1\'fd\f0 lmas\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi389\li48\ri34\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw2\b\fs22\'dd\lang1031\f0 kinci i\f1\'fe\f0 levi: \b0 Bilin\f1\'e7\f0 lenmemizin de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 ik y\f1\'f6\f0 nlerinin geli\f1\'fe\-\f0 mesini sa\f1\'f0\f0 lamak; ilgili b\f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 mde daha ayr\f1\'fd\f0 nt\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  olarak incele\-yece\f1\'f0\f0 imiz gibi, her \f1\'fe\f0 akran\f1\'fd\f0 n belli bir psikolojik i\f1\'fe\f0 levi vard\f1\'fd\f0 r.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi389\li58\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\b\fs22\'dc\'e7\'fc\lang1031\f0 nc\f1\'fc\f0  i\f1\'fe\f0 levi: \b0 Enerjiyi, de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 ik aura katlar\f1\'fd\f0  aras\f1\'fd\f0 nda \expndtw4 ta\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 mak. Her aura katman\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n, ayn\f1\'fd\f0  fiziksel v\f1\'fc\f0 cutta yer ald\f1\'fd\-\expndtw3\'f0\'fd\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde temsil edildi\f1\'f0\f0 i kendine has yedi ana \f1\'fe\f0 akra grubu \expndtw2 bulunur. Bu, her bir aura katman\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n devaml\f1\'fd\f0  bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde fre\-\expndtw4 kans oktavlar\f1\'fd\f0 nda y\f1\'fc\f0 kselerek yer almas\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  sa\f1\'f0\f0 lar. \f1\'d6\f0 rne\f1\'f0\f0 in, d\f1\'f6\f0 rd\f1\'fc\f0 nc\f1\'fc\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 akra olan kar\f1\'fd\f0 n \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 nda, asl\f1\'fd\f0 nda her biri bir \expndtw6\f1\'f6\f0 ncekinden daha y\f1\'fc\f0 ksek bir frekansa sahip yedi \f1\'fe\f0 akra var\-\expndtw2 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. Enerji, bir katmandan di\f1\'f0\f0 erine \f1\'fe\f0 akra u\f1\'e7\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0  (kalp) taraf\f1\'fd\f0 n\-\expndtw3 dan da\f1\'f0\'fd\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 r, \f1\'e7\f0 o\f1\'f0\f0 u insanda, bu noktalar s\f1\'fd\f0 k\f1\'fd\f0 ca kapal\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. On\-\expndtw5 lar\f1\'fd\f0  ruhsal safla\f1\'fe\f0 ma \f1\'e7\f0 al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 malar\f1\'fd\f0 yla, hayal etme, meditasyon \expndtw2 ve ba\f1\'fe\f0 ka al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 rmalarla (bu b\f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 mde 79. sayfaya bak\f1\'fd\f0 n), a\f1\'e7\f0 a\-\expndtw3 biliriz. B\f1\'f6\f0 ylece bunlar, bir aura katman\f1\'fd\f0 ndan di\f1\'f0\f0 erine enerji \expndtw5 aktar\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0  sa\f1\'f0\f0 larlar, \f1\'e7\'fc\f0 nk\f1\'fc\f0  u\f1\'e7\f0 ucu katmandaki \f1\'fe\f0 akralardan her\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
