\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li38\ri34\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22 Her \'fe\lang1031\f0 akra sinir sistemine ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  oldu\f1\'f0\f0 u gibi, bir hormon \expndtw3 salg\f1\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0 na da ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. \f1\'de\f0 akralar, evrensel enerjiyi (chi, prana, \expndtw7 organ, vb.) emerler ve ard\f1\'fd\f0 ndan, bunu \i nadis \i0 denen, uzun \expndtw5 enerji \f1\'fd\f0 rmaklar\f1\'fd\f0  boyunca g\f1\'f6\f0 nderirler. Bu \f1\'fd\f0 rmaklar, v\f1\'fc\f0 cudu \expndtw3 beslemek i\f1\'e7\f0 in saf enerjiyi, sinir sistemine, hormonsal salg\f1\'fd\f0 la\-\expndtw4 ra ve son olarak da kana iletirler.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li53\ri14\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw9\fs22\'de\lang1031\f0 akralann psikodinamik i\f1\'fe\f0 levi temel olarak, topra\f1\'f0\f0 a \expndtw0 ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  fiziksel, zihinsel ve duygusal ili\f1\'fe\f0 kilerle ba\f1\'f0\f0 lant\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  olan ilk \expndtw2\f1\'fc\'e7\f0  aura yap\f1\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0 yla ilgilidir. \f1\'d6\f0 rne\f1\'f0\f0 in kalp \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 , d\f1\'fc\f0 zg\f1\'fc\f0 n \f1\'e7\f0 al\f1\'fd\'fe\-\expndtw6\f0 t\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  zaman, ki\f1\'fe\f0 inin iyi bir sevgi kapasitesi, yani al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 -veri\f1\'fe\f0 i \expndtw5 olur. K\f1\'f6\f0 k \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0  iyi durumda oldu\f1\'f0\f0 unda, ki\f1\'fe\f0 i ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0  sever \expndtw3 ve topra\f1\'f0\f0 a iyice ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  oldu\f1\'f0\f0 unu hisseder. 3. g\f1\'f6\f0 z \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0  iyi \expndtw2\f1\'e7\f0 al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 nda, ki\f1\'fe\f0 i a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde (zihni a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k olarak) d\f1\'fc\'fe\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 r.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li72\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw8\fs22 A\'fe\lang1031\f0 a\f1\'f0\'fd\f0 da \f1\'fe\f0 akralann ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  olduklar\f1\'fd\f0  hormon salg\f1\'fd\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n \expndtw3 ve ayr\f1\'fd\f0 ca \f1\'fe\f0 akralann y\f1\'f6\f0 netimleri alt\f1\'fd\f0 nda bulunan v\f1\'fc\f0 cut b\f1\'f6\f0 lge\-\expndtw2 lerinin yer ald\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  bir tablo bulacaks\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z:\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
