\pard\cbpat2\li5\ri62\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw1\f1\fs22 enerji seviyelerini kald\'fd\lang1031\f0 racak g\f1\'fc\f0 ce ula\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 r. Bireyin ilerleyip ge\-\expndtw7 li\f1\'fe\f0 mesi, ayn\f1\'fd\f0  zamanda t\f1\'fc\f0 m insanl\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n geli\f1\'fe\f0 mesi demektir. \expndtw3 Bizler, ayr\f1\'fd\f0 lamaz bir b\f1\'fc\f0 t\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 n par\f1\'e7\f0 as\f1\'fd\f0 y\f1\'fd\f0 z. \f1\'d6\f0 yleyse, d\f1\'fc\f0 nyay\f1\'fd \expndtw2\f0 de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 tirmek istiyorsak, i\f1\'fe\f0 e \f1\'f6\f0 nce kendimizi de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 tirmekle ba\f1\'fe\-\expndtw4\f0 lamal\f1\'fd\f0 y\f1\'fd\f0 z. Bu \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde, d\f1\'fc\f0 nyan\f1\'fd\f0 n ne \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'e7\'fc\f0 de de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 ti\f1\'f0\f0 ini g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n\-\expndtw3 ce \f1\'fe\f0 a\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 raca\f1\'f0\'fd\f0 z.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li29\ri48\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\fs22 Her nesil do\'f0\lang1031\f0 al olarak, bir \f1\'f6\f0 nceki nesilden daha y\f1\'fc\f0 ksek \expndtw3 enerji seviyelerine dayanacak g\f1\'fc\'e7\f0 tedir. Bu \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde insanl\f1\'fd\f0 k, evrimini \f1\'e7\f0 ok daha saf bir titre\f1\'fe\f0 im seviyesine do\f1\'f0\f0 ru s\f1\'fc\f0 rd\f1\'fc\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 r.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li38\ri38\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw3\fs22\'de\lang1031\f0 imdi hep birlikte, \f1\'fe\f0 akralar\f1\'fd\f0 n v\f1\'fc\f0 cut bulmadaki (yani do\-\expndtw9\f1\'f0\f0 umdan \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 me kadar ki) geli\f1\'fe\f0 im evresini (Barbara Ann \expndtw7 Brennan'\f1\'fd\f0 n \i Hands of Light \i0 adl\f1\'fd\f0  kitab\f1\'fd\f0 ndaki ara\f1\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 rmadan \expndtw2 esinlenerek) inceleyelim.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li48\ri14\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw1\fs22\'d6\lang1031\f0 rne\f1\'f0\f0 in, ki\f1\'fe\f0 i liderlik \f1\'f6\f0 zelli\f1\'f0\f0 ini geli\f1\'fe\f0 tirmeye ihtiya\f1\'e7\f0  duya\-\expndtw2 bilir. Fiziksel d\f1\'fc\f0 nyas\f1\'fd\f0 nda, bu insan, liderlik \f1\'f6\f0 zelli\f1\'f0\f0 inin \f1\'e7\f0 ok \expndtw3\f1\'f6\f0 nemli olaca\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  ortamlarda bulunacakt\f1\'fd\f0 r. \f1\'de\f0 artlar, ki\f1\'fe\f0 iden ki\f1\'fe\f0 i\-\expndtw2 ye t\f1\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0 yle de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 iklik g\f1\'f6\f0 sterebilir ama, \f1\'f6\f0 nemli olan liderlik \expndtw1\f1\'f6\f0 zelli\f1\'f0\f0 i olacakt\f1\'fd\f0 r. \f1\'d6\f0 rne\f1\'f0\f0 in ki\f1\'fe\f0 i, y\f1\'f6\f0 netici ki\f1\'fe\f0 ilerle (politik ba\f1\'fe\-\expndtw2\f0 kanlar, \f1\'fe\f0 irket y\f1\'f6\f0 neticileri vb.) dolu bir ailede do\f1\'f0\f0 abilir. Bir \expndtw7 ba\f1\'fe\f0 kas\f1\'fd\f0 , b\f1\'f6\f0 yle y\f1\'f6\f0 netici \f1\'f6\f0 zellikleri olmayan veya k\f1\'f6\f0 t\f1\'fc\f0  olan \expndtw2 bir ailede do\f1\'f0\f0 abilir. \f1\'d6\f0 yleyse, geli\f1\'fe\f0 imi i\f1\'e7\f0 in, bu bilgilerle, zen\-\expndtw4 gin bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde donanmay\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 renmelidir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi403\li67\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\fs22 Gelecek ya\'fe\lang1031\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n planlanmas\f1\'fd\f0 nda, ruhun rehberlerin\-den alaca\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  haz\f1\'fd\f0 rl\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n derecesi onun olgunlu\f1\'f0\f0 una ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. \expndtw3 Ard\f1\'fd\f0 ndan, fiziksel ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0  i\f1\'e7\f0 in uygun ortam\f1\'fd\f0  haz\f1\'fd\f0 rlayan ebe\-\expndtw1 veynler se\f1\'e7\f0 ilir. Bu se\f1\'e7\f0 im, ruhun i\f1\'e7\f0 inde v\f1\'fc\f0 cut bulaca\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  fiziksel \expndtw5 arac\f1\'fd\f0  olu\f1\'fe\f0 turacak olan enerji kar\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  belirleyecektir. Bu \expndtw3 kar\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 m, kesinlikle bellidir ve ruha, s\f1\'f6\f0 z konusu g\f1\'f6\f0 revini yeri\-\expndtw4 ne getirmesi i\f1\'e7\f0 in, ihtiya\f1\'e7\f0  duyaca\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde yard\f1\'fd\f0 mc\f1\'fd\f0  olur.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\li490\sl-302\slmult0\cf1\lang1055\expndtw3\fs22 Ruh, \'f6\lang1031\f0 nce ki\f1\'fe\f0 isel \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 renim g\f1\'f6\f0 revini (yukar\f1\'fd\f0 daki \f1\'f6\f0 rnekteki\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\li53\sb14\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw2\fs22 liderlik \'f6\lang1031\f0 zelli\f1\'f0\f0 inin geli\f1\'fe\f0 tirilmesi gibi), sonra genel g\f1\'f6\f0 revini, \expndtw3 ard\f1\'fd\f0 ndan da evrensel g\f1\'f6\f0 revini (evren i\f1\'e7\f0 in bir \f1\'f6\f0 d\f1\'fc\f0 l) tamamla\-\expndtw5 maya haz\f1\'fd\f0 rlan\f1\'fd\f0 r. Ki\f1\'fe\f0 isel (veya \f1\'f6\f0 zel) g\f1\'f6\f0 revini tamamlarken, \expndtw3 ki\f1\'fe\f0 i evrensel g\f1\'f6\f0 revine ba\f1\'fe\f0 lamaya haz\f1\'fd\f0 rlan\f1\'fd\f0 r. Asl\f1\'fd\f0 nda ki\f1\'fe\f0 isel \expndtw4 g\f1\'f6\f0 rev, ruhunu \f1\'f6\f0 zg\f1\'fc\f0 rle\f1\'fe\f0 tirir, evrensel g\f1\'f6\f0 revini tamamlamas\f1\'fd \expndtw3\f0 i\f1\'e7\f0 in devaml\f1\'fd\f0  kullan\f1\'fd\f0 lacak olan enerjileri harekete ge\f1\'e7\f0 irir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li48\ri10\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22 Ya\'fe\lang1031\f0 am plan\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 z, se\f1\'e7\f0 im yapmam\f1\'fd\f0 z i\f1\'e7\f0 in \f1\'f6\f0 zg\f1\'fc\f0 r muhake\-\expndtw5 memizi kullanmam\f1\'fd\f0 za izin veren \f1\'e7\f0 ok say\f1\'fd\f0 da olas\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 k i\f1\'e7\f0 erir. \expndtw6 Bu, ya\f1\'fe\f0 am dokusunu olu\f1\'fe\f0 turan, sebepten sonuca bir hare\-\expndtw2 kettir. Bizler, kendi \f1\'f6\f0 z ger\f1\'e7\f0 e\f1\'f0\f0 imizi yarat\f1\'fd\f0 r\f1\'fd\f0 z.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\li432\sb302\cf1\expndtw3\b\f0\fs24\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab    \lang1055\f1 V\'fc\lang1031\f0 cut bulma\cf0\expndtw0\b0\f1\fs20\par
