\pard\cbpat2\ri120\sb10\sl-331\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw6\f1\fs22 i\'e7\lang1031\f0 in, bu bilgilerle, zengin bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde donanmay\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 renmeli\-\expndtw-6 dir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li10\ri77\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw6\fs22 Gelecek ya\'fe\lang1031\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n planlanmas\f1\'fd\f0 nda, ruhun rehberlerin\-den alaca\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  haz\f1\'fd\f0 rl\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n derecesi onun olgunlu\f1\'f0\f0 una ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. \expndtw4 Ard\f1\'fd\f0 ndan, fiziksel ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0  i\f1\'e7\f0 in uygun ortam\f1\'fd\f0  haz\f1\'fd\f0 rlayan ebe\-\expndtw2 veynler se\f1\'e7\f0 ilir. Bu se\f1\'e7\f0 im, ruhun i\f1\'e7\f0 inde v\f1\'fc\f0 cut bulaca\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  fiziksel \expndtw6 arac\f1\'fd\f0  olu\f1\'fe\f0 turacak olan enerji kar\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  belirleyecektir. Bu \expndtw3 kar\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 m, kesinlikle bellidir ve ruha, s\f1\'f6\f0 z konusu g\f1\'f6\f0 revini yeri\-\expndtw4 ne getirmesi i\f1\'e7\f0 in, ihtiya\f1\'e7\f0  duyaca\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde yard\f1\'fd\f0 mc\f1\'fd\f0  olur.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li48\ri43\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22 Ruh, \'f6\lang1031\f0 nce ki\f1\'fe\f0 isel \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 renim g\f1\'f6\f0 revini (yukar\f1\'fd\f0 daki \f1\'f6\f0 rnekte\-\expndtw1 ki liderlik \f1\'f6\f0 zelli\f1\'f0\f0 inin geli\f1\'fe\f0 tirilmesi gibi), sonra genel g\f1\'f6\f0 revini, \expndtw4 ard\f1\'fd\f0 ndan da evrensel g\f1\'f6\f0 revini (evren i\f1\'e7\f0 in bir \f1\'f6\f0 d\f1\'fc\f0 l) tamamla\-\expndtw6 maya haz\f1\'fd\f0 rlan\f1\'fd\f0 r. Ki\f1\'fe\f0 isel (veya \f1\'f6\f0 zel) g\f1\'f6\f0 revini tamamlarken, \expndtw4 ki\f1\'fe\f0 i evrensel g\f1\'f6\f0 revine ba\f1\'fe\f0 lamaya haz\f1\'fd\f0 rlan\f1\'fd\f0 r. Asl\f1\'fd\f0 nda ki\f1\'fe\f0 isel \expndtw5 g\f1\'f6\f0 rev, ruhunu \f1\'f6\f0 zg\f1\'fc\f0 rle\f1\'fe\f0 tirir, evrensel g\f1\'f6\f0 revini tamamlamas\f1\'fd \expndtw3\f0 i\f1\'e7\f0 in devaml\f1\'fd\f0  kullan\f1\'fd\f0 lacak olan enerjileri harekete ge\f1\'e7\f0 irir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi389\li82\ri29\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\fs22 Ya\'fe\lang1031\f0 am plan\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 z, se\f1\'e7\f0 im yapmam\f1\'fd\f0 z i\f1\'e7\f0 in \f1\'f6\f0 zg\f1\'fc\f0 r muhake\-\expndtw6 memizi kullanmam\f1\'fd\f0 za izin veren \f1\'e7\f0 ok say\f1\'fd\f0 da olas\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 k i\f1\'e7\f0 erir. Bu, ya\f1\'fe\f0 am dokusunu olu\f1\'fe\f0 turan, sebepten sonuca bir hare\-\expndtw2 kettir. Bizler, kendi \f1\'f6\f0 z ger\f1\'e7\f0 e\f1\'f0\f0 imizi yarat\f1\'fd\f0 r\f1\'fd\f0 z.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li101\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw8\fs22 Bir kez ruhsal rehberleriyle planlama yapt\'fd\lang1031\f0 ktan sonra \expndtw5 ruh, ruhsal d\f1\'fc\f0 nyada "bilin\f1\'e7\f0  kaybetme" evresine girer. Gebe \expndtw4 kal\f1\'fd\f0 nd\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 nda, ruhla d\f1\'f6\f0 llenmi\f1\'fe\f0  yumurta aras\f1\'fd\f0 nda bir enerji ba\-\expndtw3\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  kurulur. Ayn\f1\'fd\f0  zamanda ruhu, anneninki d\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 nda d\f1\'fd\'fe\f0  etkiler\-\expndtw5 den korumak i\f1\'e7\f0 in u\f1\'e7\f0 ucu bir kal\f1\'fd\f0 p olu\f1\'fe\f0 ur. Fiziksel bedenin \expndtw3 geli\f1\'fe\f0 imi annenin i\f1\'e7\f0 inde oldu\f1\'f0\f0 u i\f1\'e7\f0 in, ruh bu fiziksel formla \expndtw2 ba\f1\'f0\f0 lant\f1\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  gittik\f1\'e7\f0 e daha iyi alg\f1\'fd\f0 lar.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\li389\cf1\expndtw6\b\f0\fs24\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\lang1055\f1 Do\'f0\lang1031\f0 um\cf0\expndtw0\b0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi398\ri38\sb312\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22 Do\'f0\lang1031\f0 um an\f1\'fd\f0 , ruh i\f1\'e7\f0 in "e\f1\'fe\f0 siz" bir olay\f1\'fd\f0  temsil eder. O an\-\expndtw3 da, ruh u\f1\'e7\f0 ucu kal\f1\'fd\f0 b\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n korumas\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  t\f1\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0 yle kaybeder ve ilk defa olarak yeni ortam\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n etkilerine t\f1\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0 yle a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 r. Asl\f1\'fd\f0 nda \expndtw8 ruh yaln\f1\'fd\f0 zca, hepimizi \f1\'e7\f0 evreleyen enerji denizinde, pra-\expndtw10\i na'da, \i0 bulunur. Bu enerji alan\f1\'fd\f0  taraf\f1\'fd\f0 ndan etkilenirken, \expndtw4 enerji alan\f1\'fd\f0  da kendi a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0 ndan b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 yecek ve zenginle\f1\'fe\f0 ecek \expndtw8 olan bu yeni olu\f1\'fe\f0 umdan etkilenir. Bu olay t\f1\'fd\f0 pk\f1\'fd\f0 , ya\f1\'fe\f0 amda \expndtw4 var olan senfoninin ezgisine eklenen yeni bir nota gibidir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\li413\sb322\cf1\expndtw5\b\f0\fs24\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\lang1055\f1 Yeni do\'f0\lang1031\f0 mu\f1\'fe\f0  bebekler\cf0\expndtw0\b0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi389\li38\ri29\sb312\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\fs22 Do\'f0\lang1031\f0 umdan sonra, bebe\f1\'f0\f0 in fiziksel d\f1\'fc\f0 nyay\f1\'fd\f0  alg\f1\'fd\f0 lamaya \expndtw4 ba\f1\'fe\f0 lamas\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'e7\f0 ok yava\f1\'fe\f0  geli\f1\'fe\f0 ir. Yeni do\f1\'f0\f0 mu\f1\'fe\f0  bebek, daha y\f1\'fc\f0 k\-\expndtw7 sek enerjili yap\f1\'fd\f0 lara ruhunun al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 mas\f1\'fd\f0  i\f1\'e7\f0 in, \f1\'e7\f0 ok uzun s\f1\'fc\f0 re \expndtw1 uyur. B\f1\'f6\f0 ylece fiziksel ve u\f1\'e7\f0  ucu yap\f1\'fd\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 , v\f1\'fc\f0 cudunu olu\f1\'fe\f0 tur\-\expndtw4 maya u\f1\'f0\f0 ra\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 rlarken serbest b\f1\'fd\f0 rak\f1\'fd\f0 r.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li43\ri10\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw2\fs22 Bu devrede bebek, fiziksel bir v\'fc\lang1031\f0 cudun ve 3 boyutlu bir \expndtw3 d\f1\'fc\f0 nyan\f1\'fd\f0 n s\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 rlar\f1\'fd\f0 na al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 mak zorundad\f1\'fd\f0 r. Bu \f1\'e7\f0 abalama, baz\f1\'fd \expndtw4\f0 bebekler i\f1\'e7\f0 in zor bir i\f1\'fe\f0 tir. Asl\f1\'fd\f0 nda bu olay, onlar\f1\'fd\f0 n u\f1\'e7\f0 ucu d\f1\'fc\f0 nyadaki ebeveynlerine ve arkada\f1\'fe\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 na ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  kalmas\f1\'fd\f0  so\-\expndtw0 nucu zorla\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 r. Yeni ailesiyle yenilerini kurmak i\f1\'e7\f0 in, bu ba\f1\'f0\f0 lar\f1\'fd \expndtw2\f0 k\f1\'fd\f0 rmay\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 renmelidir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi379\li62\sb5\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw3\fs22 Yeni do\'f0\lang1031\f0 mu\f1\'fe\f0  bebekte, ta\f1\'e7\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'e7\f0 ok a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 kt\f1\'fd\f0 r. K\f1\'fc\'e7\'fc\f0 k v\f1\'fc\-\expndtw2\f0 cuduna uyum sa\f1\'f0\f0 lamak i\f1\'e7\f0 in u\f1\'f0\f0 ra\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 r. \f1\'dd\f0 lk \f1\'fe\f0 akray\f1\'fd\f0  - kendilerini \expndtw5 topra\f1\'f0\f0 a ba\f1\'f0\f0 layacak olan - k\f1\'f6\f0 k \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  a\f1\'e7\f0 mak i\f1\'e7\f0 in \f1\'e7\f0 ok \f1\'e7\f0 a\-\expndtw7 ba harcar. Bu k\f1\'f6\f0 k \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  a\f1\'e7\f0 ma \f1\'e7\f0 al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 mas\f1\'fd\f0  s\f1\'fc\f0 resince ruh, \expndtw3 ta\f1\'e7\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 na s\f1\'fd\f0 k s\f1\'fd\f0 k girip \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 kar. Bu devrede, k\f1\'f6\f0 k \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'e7\f0 ok \expndtw11 dar bir huniye ve ta\f1\'e7\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0  da, \f1\'e7\f0 ok b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k a\f1\'f0\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  olan bir\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\sb422\cf1\expndtw3\f0\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\lang1055\f1 56      Chislaine D. Martel\cf0\lang1031\expndtw0\f0\par
