\pard\cbpat2\fi403\li14\ri29\sb322\sl-278\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw3\fs22 7 ya\'fe\lang1031\f0 la ergenlik \f1\'e7\f0 a\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  aras\f1\'fd\f0 nda, \f1\'e7\f0 ocu\f1\'f0\f0 un zihinsel yetile-riyle, 3. \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0  olan kar\f1\'fd\f0 n \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0  ayn\f1\'fd\f0  zamanda geli\f1\'fe\f0 ir. Au-\expndtw5 ra's\f1\'fd\f0 na sar\f1\'fd\f0  renk eklenir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi389\li19\ri5\sb19\sl-283\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22 Okula ba\'fe\lang1031\f0 lamas\f1\'fd\f0 na ra\f1\'f0\f0 men \f1\'e7\f0 ocuk zihinsel yetilerini da\-\expndtw7 ha \f1\'e7\f0 ok hayal d\f1\'fc\f0 nyas\f1\'fd\f0 nda kullan\f1\'fd\f0 r. Bir K\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0 lderili \f1\'fe\f0 ef, bir \expndtw3 prens, bir kahraman olur. Dikkatli biri, \f1\'e7\f0 ocu\f1\'f0\f0 un \f1\'f6\f0 rnek ald\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd \expndtw0\f0 ki\f1\'fe\f0 ilikler arac\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 yla onun gizli arzusunu fark edebilir ve b\f1\'f6\f0 y\-\expndtw3 lece, \f1\'fc\f0 stlendi\f1\'f0\f0 i evrensel g\f1\'f6\f0 revin yap\f1\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  da a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k\f1\'e7\f0 a g\f1\'f6\f0 rebilir. \expndtw4\f1\'c7\f0 ocuklar\f1\'fd\f0 n oyunlar\f1\'fd\f0 , en derin ruhsal arzular\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n ve g\f1\'fc\f0 nl\f1\'fc\f0 k \expndtw5 ya\f1\'fe\f0 amlar\f1\'fd\f0  i\f1\'e7\f0 in belirlenmi\f1\'fe\f0  ama\f1\'e7\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n aynas\f1\'fd\f0  haline gelir. \expndtw3\f1\'d6\f0 yleyse, anne-baba ve e\f1\'f0\f0 itimci olarak, \f1\'e7\f0 ocuklar\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0 n oyun \expndtw5 odas\f1\'fd\f0 nda veya okul bah\f1\'e7\f0 esindeki hareketlerine yeni bir g\f1\'f6\f0 z\-\expndtw0 le bakmal\f1\'fd\f0 y\f1\'fd\f0 z.\cf0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li29\ri10\sb14\sl-283\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw2\fs22 Bu evredeki geli\'fe\lang1031\f0 im, ruhun v\f1\'fc\f0 cut bulmas\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n ilk evresin\-\expndtw3 de temel \f1\'fc\'e7\f0  merkezin - fiziksel, duygusal ve zihinsel - uyum \expndtw2 i\f1\'e7\f0 inde \f1\'e7\f0 al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 malar\f1\'fd\f0 na yak\f1\'fd\f0 ndan ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
