\pard\cbpat2\fi398\ri72\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\f1\fs22 Ruhsal boyuta do\'f0\lang1031\f0 ru ilerleme yolunda, daha y\f1\'fc\f0 ksek se\-\expndtw3 viyedeki enerjiler ar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 rken fiziksel boyuta ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  i\f1\'e7\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 akralar\f1\'fd\f0 -\expndtw4 n\f1\'fd\f0 n enerjisi azal\f1\'fd\f0 r. Birey, tinsel d\f1\'fc\f0 nyaya geri d\f1\'f6\f0 nmeye haz\f1\'fd\f0 r\-\expndtw5 lan\f1\'fd\f0 r. Bu do\f1\'f0\f0 al s\f1\'fc\f0 re\f1\'e7\f0  iyi anla\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 p benimsendi\f1\'f0\f0 inde, varl\f1\'fd\f0 k \expndtw3 b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k bir s\f1\'fc\f0 kunete kavu\f1\'fe\f0 ur ve ki\f1\'fe\f0 isel ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0 na sevgiyle ba\-\expndtw4 kar. Her \f1\'fe\f0 ey yerini bulmu\f1\'fe\f0  gibi g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 r. Kar\f1\'fd\f0 n \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0  daha \expndtw2 uyumlu olur. Fiziksel i\f1\'fe\f0 levlerinin azalmas\f1\'fd\f0 na ra\f1\'f0\f0 men, birey, \expndtw3 alg\f1\'fd\f0 lama duyular\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'e7\f0 ok zenginle\f1\'fe\f0 tiren bir deneyi\-me do\f1\'f0\f0 ru geli\f1\'fe\f0 ti\f1\'f0\f0 ini g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 r. \f1\'dd\'fe\f0 te bu anlatt\f1\'fd\f0 klar\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 z y\f1\'fc\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0 nden, \expndtw1 ya\f1\'fe\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  insanlara b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k bilgeliklerinden dolay\f1\'fd\f0  sayg\f1\'fd\f0  g\f1\'f6\f0 sterilir. \expndtw2 Di\f1\'f0\f0 er taraftan, bir\f1\'e7\f0 ok toplumda bu ya\f1\'fe\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  ki\f1\'fe\f0 ilere, \f1\'f6\f0 zellikle bir \expndtw5 ortakl\f1\'fd\f0 k anla\f1\'fe\f0 mas\f1\'fd\f0  gerektiren kararlar\f1\'fd\f0 n al\f1\'fd\f0 nmas\f1\'fd\f0 nda dan\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\-\expndtw-12\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 r.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
