\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li91\ri24\sb293\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22 Phoebe Bendit, \i Man Incarnate \i0 adl\'fd\lang1031\f0  kitab\f1\'fd\f0 nda, ki\f1\'fe\f0 inin fi\-ziksel ortam\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 m an\f1\'fd\f0 nda terk etti\f1\'f0\f0 i s\f1\'fd\f0 rada, parlak bir \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\-\expndtw5\'f0\'fd\f0 n ta\f1\'e7\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 ndan \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 kt\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  ileri s\f1\'fc\f0 rer. Bu kafatas\f1\'fd\f0 ndan \f1\'e7\'fd\-\expndtw3\f0 kan enerji olay\f1\'fd\f0 , s\f1\'fd\f0 k s\f1\'fd\f0 k parlak bir \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\f0 a \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 kan karanl\f1\'fd\f0 k b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k bir t\f1\'fc\f0 nelden ge\f1\'e7\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0  gibi a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 klan\f1\'fd\f0 r. "T\f1\'fc\f0 nel" ge\f1\'e7\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 i, v\f1\'fc\f0 cudun te\-\expndtw4 mel enerji ak\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 nda ruhun y\f1\'fc\f0 kselerek gezmesi gibi de a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k\-\expndtw3 lanabilir. Bu, enerji ak\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n ta\f1\'e7\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 ndan parlak \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k \f1\'fe\f0 ek\-\expndtw2 linde \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 kmak i\f1\'e7\f0 ini omurilik boyunca ilerlemesidir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li130\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22 Ruhu bu ge\'e7\lang1031\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0  s\f1\'fd\f0 ras\f1\'fd\f0 nda, \f1\'f6\f0 lm\f1\'fc\'fe\f0  ebeveynlerinin veya ar\-\expndtw2 kada\f1\'fe\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n ruhlar\f1\'fd\f0  ve tinsel rehberler kar\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 lar. B\f1\'f6\f0 ylece ki\f1\'fe\f0 i, \expndtw3 g\f1\'f6\f0 zlerinin \f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 nden t\f1\'fc\f0 m ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n, \f1\'e7\f0 ok h\f1\'fd\f0 zl\f1\'fd\f0  ve net bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekil\-de ge\f1\'e7\f0 ti\f1\'f0\f0 ini g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 r. Ki\f1\'fe\f0 i eksiksiz \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde, ba\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 ndan ge\f1\'e7\f0 en her \expndtw7\f1\'fe\f0 eyi, ald\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  kararlar\f1\'fd\f0 , \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 rendiklerini, hatta gelecek v\f1\'fc\f0 cut \expndtw24 bulmada \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 reneceklerini dahi, g\f1\'f6\f0 zden ge\f1\'e7\f0 irebilir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\li34\sb10\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw6\fs22 Rosicrucien'lere g\'f6\lang1031\f0 re, \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 mden hemen sonraki \f1\'fc\'e7\f0  g\f1\'fc\f0 n, ru\-\expndtw3 hun t\f1\'fc\f0 m ge\f1\'e7\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0  evrelerinin uyumlu bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde ger\f1\'e7\f0 ekle\f1\'fe\f0 tirme\-si i\f1\'e7\f0 in, sessiz ve huzur dolu ge\f1\'e7\f0 mesi gerekir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li19\sb14\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw7\i\fs22 Hands of Light'm \i0 yazar\'fd\lang1031\f0  Barbara Ann Brennan'\f1\'fd\f0 n ruh\-\expndtw4 sal rehberi olan Heyon'a g\f1\'f6\f0 re, \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 m s\f1\'fc\f0 reci, asl\f1\'fd\f0 nda evrensel \expndtw3 enerji alan\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n i\f1\'e7\f0 inde yer alan daha b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k bir bilin\f1\'e7\f0 lenmeye \expndtw1 do\f1\'f0\f0 ru bir ge\f1\'e7\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 tir. Bu s\f1\'fc\f0 reci \f1\'fe\'f6\f0 yle a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 klar: ki\f1\'fe\f0 i \f1\'f6\f0 ld\f1\'fc\'f0\'fc\f0 nde, bir \expndtw2 ba\f1\'fe\f0 ka boyuta do\f1\'f0\f0 ru ilerler. Bu olay kendini, enerji alan\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n \expndtw3 temizlenmesi, b\f1\'fc\f0 t\f1\'fc\f0 n \f1\'fe\f0 akralar\f1\'fd\f0 n tek tek a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0  ve safla\f1\'fe\f0 mas\f1\'fd \f0 olarak g\f1\'f6\f0 sterir. Ard\f1\'fd\f0 ndan, fiziksel boyuttaki \f1\'fc\'e7\f0  alt \f1\'fe\f0 akran\f1\'fd\f0 n \expndtw5 -k\f1\'f6\f0 k, hara ve kar\f1\'fd\f0 n- \f1\'e7\'f6\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0 lmesi gelir. Bir varl\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0 ne \expndtw3 tan\f1\'fd\f0 k olan ki\f1\'fe\f0 iler, v\f1\'fc\f0 cudu renk renk yans\f1\'fd\f0 malarla \f1\'e7\f0 evreleyen \expndtw1 bir bu\f1\'f0\f0 unun \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  fark etmi\f1\'fe\f0  olabilirler. Bu bu\f1\'f0\f0 u, enerji ya\-\expndtw3 p\f1\'fd\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n \f1\'e7\'f6\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0 lmesiyle \f1\'fc\f0 retilmi\f1\'fe\f0  enerjiden ileri gelir. Ard\f1\'fd\f0 n\-dan, \f1\'fe\f0 akralar, enerji ba\f1\'f0\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  serbest b\f1\'fd\f0 rakmak i\f1\'e7\f0 in a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 rlar. \expndtw4 Bu devrede \f1\'fc\f0 st \f1\'fe\f0 akralar di\f1\'f0\f0 er boyutlara do\f1\'f0\f0 ru b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k \expndtw2 kap\f1\'fd\f0 lar gibidirler. Sonra, alt enerji yap\f1\'fd\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 , \f1\'fc\f0 st enerji yap\f1\'fd\f0 la\-r\f1\'fd\f0 ndan ayr\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 rlar. Bu, \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 m s\f1\'fc\f0 recinin ilk evresidir.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi403\li5\ri19\sb10\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw4\fs22\'d6\lang1031\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0  izleyen ilk \f1\'fc\'e7\f0  saatte temel enerji ak\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n i\f1\'e7\f0 in\-\expndtw1 den f\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 k\f1\'fd\f0 ran enerji, ge\f1\'e7\f0 ti\f1\'f0\f0 i her yeri temizler. Bu, ruhsal vaftiz \expndtw3 gibi, v\f1\'fc\f0 cudun bir \f1\'e7\f0 e\f1\'fe\f0 it ar\f1\'fd\f0 nd\f1\'fd\f0 r\f1\'fd\f0 lmas\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. Aura, b\f1\'f6\f0 ylece alt\f1\'fd\f0 n \expndtw0 sar\f1\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0  g\f1\'fc\f0 zel bir renk al\f1\'fd\f0 r. \f1\'dd\'fe\f0 te bu enerji \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0  s\f1\'fd\f0 ras\f1\'fd\f0 nda, ki\f1\'fe\f0 inin \expndtw3 enerji merkezleri ar\f1\'fd\f0 nd\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  ve t\f1\'fc\f0 m an\f1\'fd\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'f6\f0 zg\f1\'fc\f0 r kald\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 ndan \expndtw5 b\f1\'fc\f0 t\f1\'fc\f0 n ya\f1\'fe\f0 am\f1\'fd\f0  g\f1\'f6\f0 zlerinin \f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 nden ge\f1\'e7\f0 er. Bu toparlanma s\f1\'fc\-\expndtw1\f0 recinin ba\f1\'fe\f0 lang\f1\'fd\f0 c\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. Unutma duvarlar\f1\'fd\f0  y\f1\'fd\f0 k\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 nca, ki\f1\'fe\f0 i ger\f1\'e7\f0 ek\-\expndtw2 ten kim oldu\f1\'f0\f0 unu hat\f1\'fd\f0 rlar. B\f1\'f6\f0 ylece, "\f1\'fc\f0 st ben"i veya y\f1\'fc\f0 ksek bilinciyle birle\f1\'fe\f0 ir ve bu birle\f1\'fe\f0 menin b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 kl\f1\'fc\'f0\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0  hisseder.\cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\ri29\sl-302\slmult0\qj\cf1\lang1055\expndtw5\fs22 Bu a\'e7\'fd\lang1031\f0 dan, \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 m muhte\f1\'fe\f0 em bir deneyimdir. Klinik ola\-\expndtw9 rak \f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0  kabul edilen ve bu s\f1\'fc\f0 re\f1\'e7\f0 ten ge\f1\'e7\f0 en herkes, \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k\f1\'fd\'fe \expndtw8\f0 ucunda parlak bir \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n par\f1\'fd\f0 ldad\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  bir t\f1\'fc\f0 nelden bahseder.\par
