\pard\cbpat2\li10\ri182\sb101\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\f1\fs22\'e7\lang1031\f0 evirin ve turuncu renkli \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k girdab\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n s\f1\'fd\f0 ras\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  ald\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  g\f1\'f6\-\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n... Saat y\f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 nde gitgide daha h\f1\'fd\f0 zl\f1\'fd\f0  d\f1\'f6\f0 nen bu turuncu \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k \f1\'fc\f0 zerine yo\f1\'f0\f0 unla\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 n... Gittik\f1\'e7\f0 e taze, g\f1\'fc\f0 zel bir portakala ben\-zeyerek rengi belirginle\f1\'fe\f0 iyor... Gitgide daha h\f1\'fd\f0 zl\f1\'fd\f0  d\f1\'f6\f0 nen bu turuncu \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n s\f1\'fd\f0 cakl\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  hissedin... \f1\'c7\f0 ok belirgin bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k alan\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n geni\f1\'fe\f0 ledi\f1\'f0\f0 ini hayalinizde canland\f1\'fd\f0 r\f1\'fd\f0 n...\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi389\li58\ri106\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\fs22\'de\lang1031\f0 imdi, yolculu\f1\'f0\f0 unuza biraz daha yukar\f1\'fd\f0 da, g\f1\'f6\f0 be\f1\'f0\f0 in bi\-raz \f1\'fc\f0 st\f1\'fc\f0 nde yer alan, kar\f1\'fd\f0 n \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 nda devam edin ve sar\f1\'fd \f0 bir \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n, yine saat y\f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 nde, b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k bir g\f1\'fc\f0 ne\f1\'fe\f0  gibi d\f1\'f6\f0 nd\f1\'fc\'f0\'fc\-\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0  g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n... H\f1\'fd\f0 zland\f1\'fd\f0 k\f1\'e7\f0 a gitgide kuvvetlenen bu \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n, g\f1\'fc\f0 c\f1\'fc\-\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0  ve s\f1\'fd\f0 cakl\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  hissedin... Geni\f1\'fe\f0 lemeye devam eden bu b\f1\'fc\-\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k g\f1\'fc\f0 ne\f1\'fe\f0 i hayalinizde canland\f1\'fd\f0 r\f1\'fd\f0 n... Daha sonra, bak\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd \f0 kalp \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 na \f1\'e7\f0 evirin ve kuvvetlenerek d\f1\'f6\f0 nen ye\f1\'fe\f0 il \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  izle\-yin... A\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k ye\f1\'fe\f0 il renk, girdab\f1\'fd\f0 n d\f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\'fe\f0  h\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  artt\f1\'fd\f0 k\f1\'e7\f0 a gitgide or\-man ye\f1\'fe\f0 iline d\f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\'fe\'fc\f0 yor... Ye\f1\'fe\f0 il girdap geni\f1\'fe\f0 ledik\f1\'e7\f0 e, a\f1\'fe\f0 kla ve huzurla sar\f1\'fd\f0 ld\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  hissedin...\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li130\sl-302\slmult0\lang1055\fs22\'de\lang1031\f0 imdi, bo\f1\'f0\f0 az \f1\'fe\f0 akran\f1\'fd\f0 za do\f1\'f0\f0 ru y\f1\'fc\f0 kselmeye devam edin ve gitgide daha h\f1\'fd\f0 zl\f1\'fd\f0  d\f1\'f6\f0 nen mavi \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k girdab\f1\'fd\f0 na bak\f1\'fd\f0 n... Mavi gittik\f1\'e7\f0 e geni\f1\'fe\f0 leyerek, kuvvetlendi\f1\'f0\f0 inde, bo\f1\'f0\f0 az\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  ferahlat\f1\'fd\f0 c\f1\'fd \f0 bir \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n sard\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  hissedin... \f1\'de\f0 imdi, dikkatinizi ka\f1\'fe\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z aras\f1\'fd\f0 nda yer alan 3. g\f1\'f6\f0 z \f1\'fe\f0 akras\f1\'fd\f0 na yo\f1\'f0\f0 unla\f1\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 r\f1\'fd\f0 n... Erguvan renkli \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n, her turunda daha da kuvvetlenerek, saat y\f1\'f6\-\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 nde d\f1\'f6\f0 nd\f1\'fc\'f0\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0  hayal edin... \f1\'dd\'e7\f0  g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0 n, bu erguvan girdab\f1\'fd\f0 n b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 mesiyle gittik\f1\'e7\f0 e daha netle\f1\'fe\f0 ti\f1\'f0\f0 ini hissedin... Bak\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 imdi, ba\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0 n tepesine, ta\f1\'e7\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 akran\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0 n bulundu\-\f1\'f0\f0 u yere y\f1\'f6\f0 neltin... Ve orada, kardan daha saf, pamuktan daha yumu\f1\'fe\f0 ak beyaz \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n d\f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\'fe\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0  d\f1\'fc\'fe\f0 leyin... Bir \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k ki, sizi kendi d\f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\'fe\'fc\f0 ne katarak huzurla dolduruyor... Kendinizi bu girdab\f1\'fd\f0 n merkezine \f1\'e7\f0 ekilirken hayal edin ve b\f1\'fd\f0 rak\f1\'fd\f0 n bu g\f1\'fc\f0 zel \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k sizi kaplas\f1\'fd\f0 n... Kendinizi, onun enerjisi i\f1\'e7\f0 inde\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\li5\ri62\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\fs22 akmaya b\'fd\lang1031\f0 rak\f1\'fd\f0 n... \f1\'c7\f0 ok yava\f1\'fe\'e7\f0 a, o geni\f1\'fe\f0 lemeye devam ettik\-\f1\'e7\f0 e, daha da y\f1\'fc\f0 kselin...\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li5\ri38\sb5\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\fs22\'de\lang1031\f0 imdi, fiziksel v\f1\'fc\f0 cudunuzun \f1\'fc\f0 st\f1\'fc\f0 ndesiniz... A\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k ve uyum i\f1\'e7\f0 indeki t\f1\'fc\f0 m \f1\'fe\f0 akralarla enerji dolu olan v\f1\'fc\f0 cudunuza bak\f1\'fd\f0 n... K\f1\'f6\f0 k \f1\'fe\f0 akran\f1\'fd\f0 za ve onun topra\f1\'f0\f0 a do\f1\'f0\f0 ru d\f1\'f6\f0 nen k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\-\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 na bak\f1\'fd\f0 n... \f1\'de\f0 imdi, bak\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  hara \f1\'fe\f0 akran\f1\'fd\f0 za ve turuncu renkli girdab\f1\'fd\f0 na \f1\'e7\f0 evirin... Sonra, bak\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  kar\f1\'fd\f0 n \f1\'fe\f0 akran\f1\'fd\f0 zla, onun sizi t\f1\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0 yle enerji dolu yapan b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k sar\f1\'fd\f0  g\f1\'fc\f0 ne\f1\'fe\f0 ine y\f1\'f6\-\f0 neltin... Bak\f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z \f1\'fe\f0 imdi d\f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 p duran ye\f1\'fe\f0 il \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 yla kalp \f1\'fe\f0 ak-ran\f1\'fd\f0 z \f1\'fc\f0 zerinde...\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li29\ri14\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\fs22\'de\lang1031\f0 imdi, bo\f1\'f0\f0 az \f1\'fe\f0 akran\f1\'fd\f0 za ve onun mavi \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 kl\f1\'fd\f0  girdab\f1\'fd\f0 na ba\-k\f1\'fd\f0 n... Sonra da, mor \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k girdapl\f1\'fd\f0  3. g\f1\'f6\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 ze... Girdaplar\f1\'fd\f0 n her turunda gittik\f1\'e7\f0 e daha \f1\'e7\f0 ok enerji dolan t\f1\'fc\f0 m v\f1\'fc\f0 cudunuza bak\f1\'fd\f0 n... Kendinizi hafiflemi\f1\'fe\f0  ve \f1\'f6\f0 zg\f1\'fc\f0 r hissedin... \f1\'de\f0 imdi, tek\-rar kendinizi beyaz \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k girdab\f1\'fd\f0 na b\f1\'fd\f0 rak\f1\'fd\f0 n ve v\f1\'fc\f0 cudunuz \f1\'fc\f0 ze\-rinden akt\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  hissedin... Bu yumu\f1\'fe\f0 ak beyaz \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k, v\f1\'fc\f0 cudu\-nuzu t\f1\'fc\f0 m gerginliklerden, i\f1\'e7\f0 inizde uzun zamand\f1\'fd\f0 r bulunan t\f1\'fc\f0 m engellemelerden temizliyor... B\f1\'fd\f0 rak\f1\'fd\f0 n bu beyaz \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k, yolu \f1\'fc\f0 st\f1\'fc\f0 ndeki h\f1\'fc\f0 crelerinizin herbirini temizleyen, yeniden can\-land\f1\'fd\f0 ran bir k\f1\'f6\f0 p\f1\'fc\f0 k gibi s\f1\'fc\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0 ls\f1\'fc\f0 n... Beyaz \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k, \f1\'fe\f0 imdi sizi ba\f1\'fe\-\f0 tan ba\f1\'fe\f0 a kapl\f1\'fd\f0 yor... Bu hafifli\f1\'f0\f0 i hissedin...\f1\fs20\par
