\pard\cbpat2\fi403\li19\ri134\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\fs22 Newton di\'f0\lang1031\f0 er taraftan, g\f1\'fc\f0 ne\f1\'fe\f0  \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  beyaz \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k olarak al-g\f1\'fd\f0 lamam\f1\'fd\f0 zdaki karma\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 kl\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  ke\f1\'fe\f0 fetti. \f1\'c7\f0 ok k\f1\'fc\'e7\'fc\f0 k bir aral\f1\'fd\f0 ktan karanl\f1\'fd\f0 k odaya, g\f1\'fc\f0 ne\f1\'fe\f0  \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n yatay olarak girmesini sa\f1\'f0\f0 la\-d\f1\'fd\f0 . Bu \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k huzmesinin yolu \f1\'fc\f0 st\f1\'fc\f0 ne, dik kenarl\f1\'fd\f0  cam bir priz\-ma yerle\f1\'fe\f0 tirdi. I\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 n hemen, g\f1\'f6\f0 kku\f1\'fe\f0 a\f1\'f0\'fd\f0  renklerini olu\f1\'fe\f0 turan bir \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k band\f1\'fd\f0 na d\f1\'f6\f0 n\f1\'fc\'fe\'fc\f0 verdi: mor, lacivert, mavi, ye\f1\'fe\f0 il, sar\f1\'fd\f0 , turuncu, ve k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0 . Beyaz \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k, i\f1\'fe\f0 te b\f1\'f6\f0 yle basit renklerden olu\f1\'fe\f0 mu\f1\'fe\f0 tur.\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi403\li53\ri115\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\expndtw-4\fs22 Renk, bir y\'fc\lang1031\f0 zeyde \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 ldayan \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 nlar\f1\'fd\f0 n ayr\f1\'fd\f0 lmas\f1\'fd\f0 yla olu\f1\'fe\f0 ur. Bu \expndtw-2 y\f1\'fc\f0 zey baz\f1\'fd\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  yutar ve di\f1\'f0\f0 erlerini yans\f1\'fd\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 r, bu da g\f1\'f6\f0 ze belirgin \expndtw0 bir renk izlenimini verir. \f1\'d6\f0 rne\f1\'f0\f0 in bir y\f1\'fc\f0 zey bize sar\f1\'fd\f0  g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 r, \expndtw-1\f1\'e7\'fc\f0 nk\f1\'fc\f0  buras\f1\'fd\f0  sar\f1\'fd\f0  rengi yans\f1\'fd\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 r ve di\f1\'f0\f0 er t\f1\'fc\f0 m renkleri yutar. Ge\-len t\f1\'fc\f0 m g\f1\'fc\f0 ne\f1\'fe\f0  \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 nlar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  yans\f1\'fd\f0 tan y\f1\'fc\f0 zeyler bize beyaz olarak g\f1\'f6\-\expndtw0\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 rken, t\f1\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0  yutan y\f1\'fc\f0 zeyler ise, siyah gibi g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 r.\fs20  \lang1055\f1\fs22 Se\'e7\lang1031\f0 ilmi\f1\'fe\f0  iki basit renk, birle\f1\'fe\f0 ince beyaz renk verirse; on\-lar tamamlay\f1\'fd\f0 c\f1\'fd\f0  renklerdir. Buna kar\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 k, ayn\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'fe\f0 ey "boyalar" yani, renk veren maddeler s\f1\'f6\f0 z konusu oldu\f1\'f0\f0 unda elde edi\-len renk "gri"dir, beyaz de\f1\'f0\f0 ildir. Bunlar yine de tamamlay\f1\'fd\f0 c\f1\'fd\line\pard\cbpat2\li77\ri96\sl-302\slmult0\qj\tx2976\f0 renklerdir. \f1\'dc\'e7\f0  temel renk, k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0 , sar\f1\'fd\f0  ve mavidir.\line        Sar\f1\'fd\f0        + mavi        = ye\f1\'fe\f0 il\f3\tab        \f0 k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n tamamlayan\f1\'fd\fs20\par
