\pard\cbpat2\fi394\li14\ri86\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\expndtw-6\fs24\'c7\lang1031\f0 in'de k\f1\'fd\f0 zam\f1\'fd\f0 k, \f1\'e7\f0 i\f1\'e7\f0 ek ya da k\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0 l hastal\f1\'fd\f0 klar\f1\'fd\f0 nda, hastal\f1\'fd\-\expndtw-7\'f0\'fd\f0 n a\f1\'f0\'fd\f0 rl\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  ve s\f1\'fc\f0 resini azaltmak i\f1\'e7\f0 in duvarlar k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  ka\f1\'f0\'fd\f0 t\-\expndtw0 larla kaplan\f1\'fd\f0 r veya hasta k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'f6\f0 rt\f1\'fc\f0 lere sar\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 rd\f1\'fd\f0 . Orta-\expndtw-4\f1\'e7\f0 a\f1\'f0\f0 'da \f1\'e7\f0 i\f1\'e7\f0 ek hastalar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 , k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'f6\f0 rt\f1\'fc\f0 lere sararak ve \lang1033 XVIII. \lang1055\expndtw-6\f1 y\'fc\lang1031\f0 zy\f1\'fd\f0 lda da, k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  perdelerle \f1\'e7\f0 evrilmi\f1\'fe\f0  yataklara yat\f1\'fd\f0 rarak \expndtw0 iyile\f1\'fe\f0 tirirlerdi.\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi389\li48\ri53\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\expndtw-4\fs24 Kalk\'fc\lang1031\f0 ta'da (Hindistan) hasta odalar\f1\'fd\f0 , \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n g\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 n de\f1\'f0\f0 i\-\expndtw-5\f1\'fe\f0 ik saatlerinde, duvar ve tavanda a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 lan \f1\'f6\f0 zel aral\f1\'fd\f0 klardan gir\-\expndtw-2 mesi sa\f1\'f0\f0 lanacak \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde in\f1\'fe\f0 a edilirdi. Bu a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 kl\f1\'fd\f0 klar, renkli cam veya ipek \f1\'f6\f0 rt\f1\'fc\f0 lerle s\f1\'fc\f0 slenirdi. Alt\f1\'fd\f0  renk, bazen iki iki \expndtw-7 ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  olarak kullan\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 rd\f1\'fd\f0 . Beyaz \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 k, ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  oldu\f1\'f0\f0 u di\f1\'f0\f0 er rengin etkisini de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 tirmek veya hafifletmek i\f1\'e7\f0 in kullan\f1\'fd\f0 labiliyordu. \expndtw-5 Bug\f1\'fc\f0 n, de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 ik terapistler \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 kla \f1\'e7\f0 al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 man\f1\'fd\f0 n yararlar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  tekrar \expndtw-4 ke\f1\'fe\f0 fediyorlar ve bunlar\f1\'fd\f0 , tedavilerinde gittik\f1\'e7\f0 e daha ba\f1\'fe\f0 ar\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd \expndtw0\f0 bir \f1\'fe\f0 ekilde kullan\f1\'fd\f0 yorlar.\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\li62\sb312\qc\lang1055\expndtw-14\b\fs24 TABAKTAK\'dd\lang1031\f0  RENKLER\expndtw0\b0\f1\fs20\par
\pard\cbpat2\fi389\li106\sb302\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\expndtw-6\fs24 Renkler konusunda \'fe\lang1031\f0 imdiye kadar \f1\'f6\'f0\f0 rendiklerimizi, ayn\f1\'fd \expndtw-8\'fe\f0 ekilde besin se\f1\'e7\f0 imimizde kullanabilir ve b\f1\'f6\f0 ylece, sa\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd \expndtw-4\f0 geri kazanmak ve korumak konusunda daha ba\f1\'fe\f0 ar\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  olabili\-\expndtw-6 riz. \f1\'d6\f0 rne\f1\'f0\f0 in zay\f1\'fd\f0 f ve kans\f1\'fd\f0 z biri, pancar, domates, k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  la\-hana vs. gibi k\f1\'fd\f0 rm\f1\'fd\f0 z\f1\'fd\f0  yiyecekleri se\f1\'e7\f0 erek eski g\f1\'fc\f0 c\f1\'fc\f0 ne kavu\f1\'fe\f0 a\-\expndtw-5 bilir. Di\f1\'f0\f0 er taraftan stresli biri, ye\f1\'fe\f0 il sebzelerden olu\f1\'fe\f0 an bir \expndtw-7 b\f1\'fc\f0 feyle sakin bir k\f1\'fd\f0 r ortam\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n tad\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  \f1\'e7\'fd\f0 karabilir. Yine, salata\-\expndtw-4 n\f1\'fd\f0 zda g\f1\'f6\f0 kku\f1\'fe\f0 a\f1\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n t\f1\'fc\f0 m renklerini kullanarak renklerin en a\f1\'e7\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 ndan en koyusuna kadar var olan d\f1\'fc\f0 zeninin t\f1\'fc\f0 m \f1\'f6\f0 zel\-\expndtw0 liklerinden yararlanabiliriz.\f1\fs20\par
