\pard\cbpat2\fi398\li48\sb312\sl-302\slmult0\qj\lang1055\f1\fs22 Dussaud'a g\'f6\lang1031\f0 re, yedi m\f1\'fc\f0 zik notas\f1\'fd\f0  aras\f1\'fd\f0 nda var olan tit\-re\f1\'fe\f0 im ba\f1\'f0\f0 lant\f1\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0 yla, renk spektrumundaki de\f1\'f0\f0 i\f1\'fe\f0 ik renkler aras\f1\'fd\f0 nda bulunan titre\f1\'fe\f0 im ba\f1\'f0\f0 lant\f1\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0  ayn\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. \f1\'c7\'fd\f0 nlamal\f1\'fd\f0  gam\f1\'fd\f0 n ve \f1\'fd\'fe\'fd\f0 lt\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0  gam\f1\'fd\f0 n g\f1\'fc\f0 zelli\f1\'f0\f0 ini sa\f1\'f0\f0 layan ayn\f1\'fd\f0  say\f1\'fd\f0 lard\f1\'fd\f0 r. Bu say\f1\'fd\-\f0 lar: 24, 27, 30, 32, 36, 40 ve 45'tir. Ayn\f1\'fd\f0  say\f1\'fd\f0 lar\f1\'fd\f0 , g\f1\'f6\f0 ky\f1\'fc\-\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0 nde, y\f1\'fd\f0 ld\f1\'fd\f0 zlarla \f1\'e7\f0 evrelerinde d\f1\'f6\f0 nen gezegenler aras\f1\'fd\f0 ndaki uzakl\f1\'fd\f0 kta ve atomun \f1\'e7\f0 ekirde\f1\'f0\f0 inden elektronlar\f1\'fd\f0  ay\f1\'fd\f0 ran ara\-l\f1\'fd\f0 kta da buluruz. Baudelaire'in \f1\'fe\f0 iirindeki gibi, en b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 kten en k\f1\'fc\'e7\'fc\'f0\f0 e renkler, sesler, tatlar ve kokular orant\f1\'fd\f0 l\f1\'fd\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r. Bu ev\-rensel bir uyumu i\f1\'fe\f0 aret g\f1\'f6\f0 sterir.\f1\fs20\par
