\pard\cbpat2\fi379\li355\sl-312\slmult0\lang1055\fs22 Brown \'dc\lang1031\f0 niversitesi'nde dilbilimci olan Dr. Philip Lieber-man'\f1\'fd\f0 n ara\f1\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 rmalar\f1\'fd\f0 na g\f1\'f6\f0 re, her birey "\f1\'f6\f0 zel bir i\f1\'fe\f0 aret" ile\fs20  \lang1055\f1\fs22 donat\'fd\lang1031\f0 lm\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 r; bu i\f1\'fe\f0 aret o ki\f1\'fe\f0 inin duygular\f1\'fd\f0 na i\f1\'fe\f0 aret eder. Da\-ha \f1\'f6\f0 nce de g\f1\'f6\f0 rd\f1\'fc\'f0\'fc\f0 m\f1\'fc\f0 z gibi, duygular \f1\'fe\f0 akralar\f1\'fd\f0 m\f1\'fd\f0 za ba\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\-\f0 d\f1\'fd\f0 r, demek ki ki\f1\'fe\f0 inin ses t\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 s\f1\'fd\f0 na g\f1\'f6\f0 re kolayl\f1\'fd\f0 kla sa\f1\'f0\f0 l\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0  konu\-sunda bir tan\f1\'fd\f0  konulabilir.\f1\fs20\par
