\pard\cbpat2\fi394\ri10\sb302\sl-307\slmult0\qj\expndtw-6\fs24 D\'fc\'fe\'fc\lang1031\f0 nce, madde i\f1\'e7\f0 inde kendini g\f1\'f6\f0 steren hafif, h\f1\'fd\f0 zl\f1\'fd\f0  ve \expndtw-3 hareketli bir enerji \f1\'fe\f0 eklidir. D\f1\'fc\'fe\'fc\f0 nce, bir \f1\'fe\f0 eklin g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 nt\f1\'fc\f0 s\f1\'fc\-\expndtw-6\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 n, fiziksel enerjisini kullanarak zamanla fiziksel planda g\f1\'f6\-\expndtw-7\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 nd\f1\'fc\'f0\'fc\f0  bir bi\f1\'e7\f0 im (fikir) yarat\f1\'fd\f0 r. \f1\'dd\f0 nsan oldu\f1\'f0\f0 umuz i\f1\'e7\f0 in, bizler \expndtw-3 her \f1\'fe\f0 eyden \f1\'f6\f0 nce birer "g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 nt\f1\'fc\f0  \f1\'fc\f0 reticisi"yiz.\lang1055\expndtw0\f1\fs20\par
