\pard\cbpat2{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent278{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-278\li816\sl-293\slmult0\qj\tx816\expndtw-2\b Yo\'f0\lang1031\f0 unla\f1\'fe\f0 ma. \b0 V\f1\'fc\f0 cudunuzun ve zihninizin sakin ve \expndtw-4 a\f1\'e7\'fd\f0 k oldu\f1\'f0\f0 u \f1\'fe\f0 u anda yo\f1\'f0\f0 unla\f1\'fe\f0 ma al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 rmalar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  yap\-maya haz\f1\'fd\f0 rs\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z. Bu al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 rmalar, g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 nt\f1\'fc\f0 lerinize ha\-\expndtw-5 kim olman\f1\'fd\f0 z i\f1\'e7\f0 in, i\f1\'e7\f0  g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0  keskinle\f1\'fe\f0 tirmek amac\f1\'fd\-\expndtw-4\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  ta\f1\'fe\'fd\f0 r. Zihinsel g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 nt\f1\'fc\f0 ler \f1\'fc\f0 zerinde m\f1\'fc\f0 kemmel bir \expndtw-2 kontrol kurmak, i\f1\'e7\f0  g\f1\'f6\f0 r\f1\'fc\f0 n\f1\'fc\f0 z\f1\'fc\f0  a\f1\'e7\f0 mak i\f1\'e7\f0 in, g\f1\'f6\f0 z ve zi\-\expndtw-3 hin jimnasti\f1\'f0\f0 inden ba\f1\'fe\f0 ka bir \f1\'fe\f0 ey de\f1\'f0\f0 ildir. Daha \f1\'f6\f0 nce \expndtw-4 7. B\f1\'f6\f0 l\f1\'fc\f0 m'de, yo\f1\'f0\f0 unla\f1\'fe\f0 ma \f1\'fc\f0 zerinde \f1\'e7\f0 al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\'f0\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 za g\f1\'f6\f0 re, \expndtw-3 a\f1\'fe\f0 a\f1\'f0\'fd\f0 daki al\f1\'fd\'fe\f0 t\f1\'fd\f0 rmalar\f1\'fd\f0  yaparken b\f1\'fc\f0 y\f1\'fc\f0 k bir kolayl\f1\'fd\f0 k \expndtw0 ya\f1\'fe\f0 ayacaks\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 z.\lang1055\f1\par
