\pard\cbpat2{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent163{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi389\li53\ri29\sl-302\slmult0\qj\tx605\b Ba\'fe\lang1031\f0 kalar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n duygular\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  anlayabilme: \b0 Yarat\f1\'fd\f0 c\f1\'fd \f0 ki\f1\'fe\f0 i, ba\f1\'fe\f0 kalar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n duygular\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0  anlama, "kendini ba\f1\'fe\f0 kalar\f1\'fd\f0 n\f1\'fd\f0 n yerine koyma" yetene\f1\'f0\f0 ine sahiptir.\lang1055\f1\par
